00:28:50.680 --> 00:28:56.020
But his decline was
precipitated by becoming addicted

00:28:56.020 --> 00:28:58.990
to narcotics, falling into crime.

00:28:58.990 --> 00:29:04.030
Instead of his name appearing on
the back page for his headlines,

00:29:04.030 --> 00:29:11.390 position:56%
