00:33:42.390 --> 00:33:45.420
Back then, the most powerful person

00:33:45.420 --> 00:33:50.540
in high school basketball was not
Nike, not Under Armour, not Adidas.

00:33:50.540 --> 00:33:54.100
It was a gentleman by the
name of Howard Garfinkel,

00:33:54.100 --> 00:33:58.160
who ran the Five-Star
Basketball Camps.

00:33:58.160 --> 00:34:03.210
And so what would happen was, Coach
Wade would put these guys in a van.

00:34:03.210 --> 00:34:06.910
They would drive up to
Pennsylvania to participate

00:34:06.910 --> 00:34:09.390 position:56%
in these Five-Star Basketball Camps.

00:34:09.390 --> 00:34:13.900
The director of the drills
and the teaching was a guy

00:34:13.900 --> 00:34:16.200
by the name of Bobby Knight.

00:34:16.200 --> 00:34:19.730
Young coaches who were still
in high school at the time,

00:34:19.730 --> 00:34:26.940 position:56%
begging for a college job, like Dick
