00:34:35.840 --> 00:34:41.160
So picture Bob Wade driving
a van up to Five-Star,

00:34:41.160 --> 00:34:45.320
and all of these long limbed
individuals get out the van.

00:34:45.320 --> 00:34:49.320
Howard Garfinkel runs up to Wade,
and his nickname for him was sugar.

00:34:49.320 --> 00:34:53.730
And he'd say, sugar, I hear
you're keeping all these secrets

00:34:53.730 --> 00:34:56.840
down in Baltimore.

00:34:56.840 --> 00:35:00.410
And so Howard Garfinkel and
Wade actually almost got

00:35:00.410 --> 00:35:02.720
