Ralph Sampson, Len Bias.

00:36:11.890 --> 00:36:15.120
No one had a five-foot-three-inch
horse.

00:36:16.130 --> 00:36:18.930
So they had to be separated.

00:36:18.930 --> 00:36:22.830 position:56%
And Garfinkel says, you're screwing
