00:36:48.400 --> 00:36:50.330
up the top-rated point
guard in the country.

00:36:50.330 --> 00:36:54.940
Did not sleep the night before
he had to play against him.

00:36:54.940 --> 00:36:58.940
And for the first time in his
career, he was talking to himself

00:36:58.940 --> 00:37:02.860
when Muggsy was guarding him,
saying, keep the ball tight,

00:37:02.860 --> 00:37:07.320
don't let them steal it,
don't let them embarrass you.

00:37:07.320 --> 00:37:13.910 position:56%
And after that camp, was when
Muggsy became a national phenomenon.

00:37:13.910 --> 00:37:18.000
And in Howard Garfinkel's Five-Star
report that he sent out to all

00:37:18.000 --> 00:37:23.160
of the top college coaches, he
gave Muggsy a Five-Star rating,

00:37:23.160 --> 00:37:26.560
